<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ticket de Soporte - Zypher</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="ticket.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap');

        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #1e1e2e 0%, #16283d 100%);
            color: #ecf0f1;
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin: 0;
            color: #f1c40f;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        header p {
            margin-top: 5px;
            font-size: 1em;
            color: #bdc3c7;
        }

        header a {
            color: #f1c40f;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Main container */
        .ticket-container {
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0px 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #3498db;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        p {
            color: #bdc3c7;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .ticket-form {
            text-align: left;
        }

        .ticket-form label {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: block;
            color: #f1c40f;
        }

        input, textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background-color: #2e3a47;
            border: 1px solid #3498db;
            border-radius: 8px;
            color: #ecf0f1;
            font-size: 1em;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        input:focus, textarea:focus {
            border-color: #f1c40f;
            outline: none;
        }

        button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #2980b9;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .back-link {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .back-link a {
            color: #f1c40f;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .back-link a:hover {
            color: #f39c12;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: #bdc3c7;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-top: auto;
            box-shadow: 0px -2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <header>
        <h1>Zypher Soporte</h1>
        <p><a href="/">Volver a la página principal</a></p>
    </header>

    <!-- Ticket Form Container -->
    <div class="ticket-container">
        <h2>Crear Ticket de Soporte</h2>
        <p>Describe tu problema o consulta y nuestro equipo se pondrá en contacto contigo lo antes posible.</p>

        <form class="ticket-form">
            <label for="titulo">Asunto</label>
            <input type="text" id="titulo" name="titulo" placeholder="Escribe el asunto" required>

            <label for="descripcion">Descripción</label>
            <textarea id="descripcion" name="descripcion" rows="5" placeholder="Describe el problema o pregunta detalladamente" required></textarea>

            <button type="submit">Enviar Ticket</button>
        </form>

        <div class="back-link">
            <p><a href="/">← Volver al Soporte</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Zypher Soporte. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
